        <h3>
            Multi-Value Form &amp; Search Dropdown</h1>
            <hr>
            <p>
                This is my example of how to combine
                <b>hidden-form-controls.js</b> and
                <b>hidden-list-search.js</b> into a single html form.
                This allows for a form that a user can add one or more
                values, and each unique value appears as a cancellable
                tag.  These are then submitted with the form all under
                the same input name.
            </p>
            <p>
                This can be used for multiple input on the same
                page by providing unique id's for each required
                element and a unique name for each input value.
            </p>
    </div>
